    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯公司以 28 亿美元收购竞争对手 Stelco</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司 (Cleveland-Cliffs Inc.) 同意以约 38.5 亿加元（28 亿美元）收购加拿大钢铁制造商 Stelco Holdings Inc.，这是该公司在去年竞购美国钢铁公司失败后的首次重大举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德资产规模创 10.6 万亿美元新高，受 ETF 提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/blackrock-hits-10-6-trillion-asset-record-reports-etf-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司第二季度向其长期投资基金注入了 510 亿美元的客户现金，使这家全球最大的资金管理公司的资产达到创纪录的 10.6 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/blackrock-hits-10-6-trillion-asset-record-reports-etf-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 6 月份贸易逆差因进口费用下降而缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/india-trade-gap-in-june-narrows-as-import-bill-shrinks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于印度控制了进口费用且全球需求有所复苏，出口保持稳定，印度 6 月份贸易逆差有所缩小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/india-trade-gap-in-june-narrows-as-import-bill-shrinks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:33:55 GMT</pubDate>
